high_descs: Go around the kitchen island and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the knife out of the sink.
Turn around and face the apple next to the microwave.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Turn around and face the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and face the apple slices.
Pick up an apple slice from the counter.
Turn around and face the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave and then take it back out.
Go around the fridge and race the center island.
Set the apple slice on the center island.
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple, cook it, then set it on the center island.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen sink
Pick up the knife on the right in the sink
Cut the apple on the counter to the right of the sink next to the microwave
Move a step back from the counter
Turn around and face the microwave
Place the knife inside the microwave
Turn around and face the same counter with the cut apple
Pick up a piece of the apple
Turn around and face the microwave
Place the apple piece in the microwave, turn it on for a few seconds, and take the apple piece out
Turn around and go to the kitchen island
Place the apple piece on the top of the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, warm a piece of the apple, and place it on the kitchen island

high_descs: Turn left and head to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the sink.
Turn completely around and go to the microwave.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Turn towards the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the counter with the sliced apple.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Go back to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave, cook the apple and pick it back up.
Turn right, go halfway across the room and turn right toward the table.
Put the slice of apple on the table to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of apple on the table.
